    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's honestly exhausting thinking about everything. like, in a billion years the sun is just gonna swallow the earth and it won't even matter that we ever existed. everything we do, all the pain and the struggle... it's just such a cosmic joke. what's even the point of trying to keep going when the end result is just nothingness anyway?",
